    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Giving widgets control over the search means that any of them could mess up with the lifecycle of the other. It will be then very hard to reason about InstantSearch. And there is a solution for the problem. So I will close this issue for now (please open a new one if need be).\r\n\r\nThanks for your contribution, this is always appreciated.",
